description: Ever wondered why your Dog goes WACKO™ for a SCHMACKOS™ Treat? It's because SCHMACKOS treats are specifically designed to smell and taste absolutely amazing... to a dog.It's this yumminess that is at the heart of the SCHMACKOS Brand philosophy. The philosophy to do everything possible to help dogs and their humans have more fun together. That's why we've created an irresistible range of dog treats that are perfect for playing, training, rewarding and occupying our fury friends.STRAPZ™ TREATS are baked then air dried to seal in the delicious flavour of real meat. Available in a variety of flavours including Beef, Liver and Chicken.-REAL MEAT RECIPE-95% FAT FREE-No added artificial flavours-Australian Made  -SUITABLE FOR PUPPIES OVER 6 MONTHS OF AGE, ADULT & SENIOR DOGS
